<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天早上，乐购超市的两个工作人员正在给货架上货。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“梅格，我们的罐装番茄酱太多了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个工作人员看了看箱子说，“货架上放不下。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就放在收银台旁边吧。”梅格说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得快点儿，超市马上要开门了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们搬着箱子走在过道上，梅格发现一些货架空着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46430</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们刚才明明把这里的货架都放满了，食物都去哪儿了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>达里尔的脚下嘎吱一声，他低头一看，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>面包屑和包装纸散落在地板上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是你一直在吃东西吗，达里尔？”梅格放下箱子问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然不是！”达里尔回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是谁在吃东西？”哼哼！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>达里尔吓了一跳，箱子掉在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是什么声音？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>梅格指了指过道的尽头，他们小心翼翼地往那边走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哼哼！突然一个巨大的身影跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”梅格和达里尔跑开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰克，你在做什么？”艾普卡特老师皱了皱眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克在地板上爬着：“我的铅笔从桌子上掉下来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西捡起铅笔：“给你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老师双臂交叉，表情很严厉：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你应该安静地看书，而不是找铅笔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克坐下来，转着他的铅笔：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的书没意思，真希望现在是休息时间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的书很有意思。”特勒尔说，“是讲丝绸之路的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的书也没意思吗？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“书挺有意思的，不过我太饿了。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好想快点吃午饭，今天吃披萨。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我都闻到香味了。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克吸了吸鼻子：“我也闻到了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾普卡特老师皱了皱眉：“嘘！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克不好意思地笑了笑：“对不起！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“艾普卡特老师，我要……嗯……去一下洗手间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跑到走廊上，她打开手表：“布洛姆市长，怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿。”布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“美罗城有一个偷食物的小偷。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“偷食物的小偷？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长点了点头：“小偷没付钱就吃了食物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会去看看，市长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，我一直都是和危险的坏人战斗，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而不是和那些吃了一顿饭不付钱的人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个小偷不是只吃了一顿饭。”布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他把乐购超市里的所有食物都吃光了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天呐！”罗西大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，他还把另外两家食品店和几家餐厅的食物也都吃光了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长摇了摇头，“他现在在美罗城面包店。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个小偷听起来像个超级大胃王。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长。我马上出发！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253430</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当罗西到达时，警察已经包围了美罗城面包店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探正站在一辆警车后面观察。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飘到史密斯侦探旁边：“嗨，侦探先生！听说你今天的胃口很大。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很有意思，火箭女孩儿。”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吃了所有食物的人可不是我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，那是谁？”罗西问，“你有那个小偷的资料吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探看了一眼他的笔记本：“我采访了乐购超市的两个工作人员，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们说小偷是个巨大的……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！面包店的门炸开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰尘落下来以后，一个巨大的身影走了出来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西大吃一惊：“一头巨大的猪！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>